= 2004-09 PricewaterhouseCoopers: software patents a major threat to Europe =
--> 
[ [:SwpatsiskuEn: Studies]
| [http://swpat.ffii.org/xatra/cons0406/parl/ Studies (short)] 
| [:DB040622En: Deutsche Bank 2004-06-22]
